Logging
===========

kubectl logs -f <pod_name>


Multi-container pod log filtering
================================

kubectl logs -f <pod_name> <specific_container_name>




Monitoring
==============


Node - > Kubelet -> contains CAdvisor => retrieves performance metrics for kubernetes pods

kubectl top node // cpu and memory for each of the nodes

kubectl top pod // performance metrics for pods

